  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0106": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0106",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0106a",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "俺は精液まみれの妻たちを優しく、しかし貪欲に抱いていった。\n他の男に何度も犯された身体を、丁寧に愛撫し、キスを浴びせ、深く繋がる。"
    },
    "FadeData": {
      "IsFadeIn": true,
      "IsFadeOut": false
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0106a": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0106a",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0107",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "俺たちの夜は、まだまだ長く続いた……"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0107": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0107",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0108",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "他人の目には、俺たちの関係は歪んで見えるかもしれない。\nだが、これが俺たち夫婦の愛の形だ。"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0108": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0108",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "他の男とセックスを楽しんでいても、彼女たちの心はいつも俺のものだ。　どんなに乱れても、彼女たちは必ず俺の元へ戻ってくる。"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109a",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "そして俺は、そんな彼女たちを心の底から愛している。"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109a": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109a",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109b",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "他の男に犯される妻。\n精液まみれの妻。\n肉便器として悦ぶ妻。"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109b": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0109b",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0110",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "そんな彼女たちのすべてが、俺は大好きだ。"
    }
  },

  "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0110": {
    "ID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0110",
    "Type": "Talk",
    "WaitingType": "Click",
    "NextStepID": "eee_post_yotogi_common_bedroom_0111",
    "TalkData": {
      "SpecificSpeaker": "Narrative",
      "Text": "これが俺と彼女たちの、特別な「愛」の形なのだ。"
    }
  },
